{"tid":736611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"首次有考生因作弊被取消所有中學文憑試科目成績","createTime":"2018-07-10T10:55:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T12:33:40.000Z","uid":147522,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cfd6fb92715d99f28552d43e270ccfc3f2e1d0b2","tid":736611,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:55:20.000Z","msg":"中學文憑試明日放榜，今年首次有考生因作弊，被取消所有科目的考試成績。<br />\n<br />\n有一名考生被發現於考試期間，身上藏有大量與應考科目有關的筆記及小紙條，被定為嚴重違規。試場主任要求對方交出身上物品，該名考生亦承認有關行為，被考評局定為蓄意作弊，並取消文憑試所有科目成績。<br />\n<br />\n另外，考評局今年接獲79宗違反手提電話規則的個案，與去年相若，當中有兩名考生成績被降級。<br />\n<br />\n考評局公開考試總監李王鍏表示，今年有很多考生在不知情下，被家長將手機放進書包，亦有家長在口試期間致電關心考生。李王鍏提醒家長關心子女考試情況，宜改善溝通，盡量避免在考生到達考場後致電。"},{"pid":"51cbf9c4e5ec76da6b20484c21809a41c1f9dd19","tid":736611,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:57:08.000Z","msg":"出年再考啦"},{"pid":"b5bf81ec58facecb886746de2ec243357d4bc440","tid":736611,"uid":9542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:57:42.000Z","msg":"應該得弱智先會信"},{"pid":"93679d61fc959aa28d8689e224c7677465b8c44d","tid":736611,"uid":9542,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:58:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote> 今年有很多考生在不知情下，被家長將手機放進書包</blockquote><br />\n應該得弱智先會信"},{"pid":"d665c3734954414f14fd53ee2a41173f6f8015e8","tid":736611,"uid":35014,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:58:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51540d5114e95662c5b1f707c8b3dcd3ec649933","tid":736611,"uid":69761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:58:47.000Z","msg":"被家長將手機放進書包"},{"pid":"8366fe9fab49fef141629e87fe063c2342d9f665","tid":736611,"uid":163149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:59:08.000Z","msg":"今年有很多考生在不知情下，被家長將手機放進書包<br />\n<br />\n幼稚園學生？"},{"pid":"451f298f075b252a2689336f06d81649e5daf5a4","tid":736611,"uid":35919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:00:27.000Z","msg":"電話個藉口咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf8e144bd50495394499cead9a1ad98c1bb6b465","tid":736611,"uid":3457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8366fe9fab49fef141629e87fe063c2342d9f665","tid":736611,"uid":163149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T10:59:08.000Z","msg":"今年有很多考生在不知情下，被家長將手機放進書包<br />\n<br />\n幼稚園學生？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"唔出奇 帶埋老母見工都有 <br />\n冇咩奇怪"},{"pid":"2250650c3742a741b779095c3398089400851c8b","tid":736611,"uid":43808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:02:14.000Z","msg":"手機被家長放入去，小學生咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c43311d2d7fd7c33fef3212ada0f21091ed505","tid":736611,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T11:14:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"99b0a75ae3fba58985a53c2672fbc1cc16cfc4ff","tid":736611,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T12:33:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}